      "content": "but what if there's no \"rest\" that changes it? i've tried just sitting in the silence, and it doesn't feel peaceful. it just feels like i'm staring at a life that finished its story a long time ago. it feels like i'm just an echo of someone who actually mattered. does it even make sense to keep dragging this shell around if the spark is never coming back?",
